# 🌍 AI Language Translator

## 📌 Overview

AI Language Translator is a web-based application developed as part of my CodeAlpha Internship. The project enables users to translate text between multiple languages in real time using AI-powered translation services.

The application provides a simple and intuitive interface where users can enter text, select source and target languages, and instantly receive accurate translations. The project demonstrates API integration, frontend development, and the implementation of AI-powered language processing features.

## ✨ Features

* 🌐 Translate text between multiple languages
* 🤖 AI-Powered Translation
* ⚡ Fast and Real-Time Results
* 📱 Responsive Design
* 🎨 Modern User Interface
* 📋 Easy Text Input and Output
* 🔄 Language Selection Support

## 🛠️ Technologies Used

* HTML5
* CSS3
* JavaScript
* AI Translation API
* Git & GitHub

## 🎯 Project Objective

The objective of this project was to build an intelligent language translation tool that allows users to communicate across different languages efficiently while gaining hands-on experience with API integration and AI-powered applications.

## 📚 Learning Outcomes

Through this project, I gained practical experience in:

* API Integration
* Artificial Intelligence Applications
* Frontend Web Development
* JavaScript Programming
* Responsive Web Design
* User Interface Development
* Problem Solving and Debugging

## 🚀 Future Enhancements

* Voice Input Support
* Text-to-Speech Functionality
* Language Auto Detection
* Translation History
* Dark/Light Theme Toggle

